              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="content-card">
            <div class="year-badge">2012</div>
            <h3>Established</h3>
            <p>Established and began serving WN manpower outsourcing services.</p>
            <div class="card-footer">
              <span class="tag">Founding</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="timeline-item" data-year="2013">
