      </div>

      <div class="timeline-item" data-year="2019">
        <div class="timeline-item-content left">
          <div class="timeline-dot">
            <div class="node-icon">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path d="M17 17l5-5-5-5M3 8h13M3 16h13" />
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="content-card">
            <div class="year-badge">2019</div>
            <h3>EDC Expansion</h3>
            <p>Extended services to EDC business segment and won the DANA partnership.</p>
            <div class="card-footer">
              <span class="tag">Partnership</span>
            </div>
